{"tid":1580370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"921冷處理，咩都唔好做","createTime":"2019-09-19T04:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:15:27.000Z","uid":4200,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e35d7235920d6b7922cd8b0bb3bedc962b43e539","tid":1580370,"uid":4200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"原因: 中共圈套黎，想我地群眾鬥群眾，跟住淨係得手足比人拉。然後轉移焦點，令我地犯錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔做野有咩好處: <br />\n1:成班愛國者係度搗亂，商舖落閘，間接幫我地打擊經濟<br />\n2:我地唔去干涉，就唔會忍唔住還拖，黑警就冇得拉人<br />\n3:黑警對住愛國者搗亂都唔做野，可以幫我地輿論上彈<br />\n<br />\n唔做野有咩壞處: <br />\n1:除左勇武手足周身唔自在之外，基本上沒有<br />\n2:連儂牆被撕，不過好少事，撕一貼百<br />\n<br />\n相反921出黎應戰或反擊會有以下風險，中正中共圈套：<br />\n1.手足被打然後拉，對面可能咩事都冇<br />\n2.唔知點解對面有人訓底左，影響觀感，嚴重可能會引起美國法案產生變數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以最好咩都唔好做，黑衫都唔使著，唔好守醬。最緊要後生手足咪落單。"},{"pid":"056e30f53c448385fa437e1bb76b939e2ca4661b","tid":1580370,"uid":4200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"幫襯小店，番屋企訓覺"},{"pid":"edde76b44ee11b279d46a14b93265a10f19adc52","tid":1580370,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"一定要推到全世界知"},{"pid":"72f1b11b1f450f7739ed1dd94bdec868843b2656","tid":1580370,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"去睇娜娜啦"},{"pid":"b9cecf53bb73814e372004ae1b4e4bb8b0b9fed7","tid":1580370,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屯門再光復呀</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆咪尤佢拆<br />\n拆完夜晚痴番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc3f28a2aadbe838a251dce49b94a144f2ddb8","tid":1580370,"uid":4200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9cecf53bb73814e372004ae1b4e4bb8b0b9fed7","tid":1580370,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"<stro